sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / Data Scientist
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Webhook as Spark Webhook<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Controller as Spark Controller<br/>8080/TCP metrics
    participant SparkSubmit as spark-submit<br/>(local process)
    participant Driver as Spark Driver Pod
    participant Executors as Spark Executor Pods
    participant ConnectSvc as SparkConnect Service<br/>15002/TCP gRPC
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus<br/>8080/TCP HTTP

    rect rgb(230, 240, 255)
        Note over User,Executors: Flow 1: SparkApplication Submission
        User->>K8sAPI: POST SparkApplication CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token / kubeconfig
        K8sAPI->>Webhook: Mutate SparkApplication<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS, API server client cert
        Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Mutated (defaults applied)
        K8sAPI->>Webhook: Validate SparkApplication<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS, API server client cert
        Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Validated
        K8sAPI-->>User: SparkApplication created

        Controller->>K8sAPI: Watch SparkApplication<br/>443/TCP HTTPS, SA token
        K8sAPI-->>Controller: SparkApplication event

        Controller->>SparkSubmit: Execute spark-submit<br/>(process exec)
        SparkSubmit->>K8sAPI: Create Driver Pod<br/>443/TCP HTTPS, SA token (spark-operator-spark)

        K8sAPI->>Webhook: Mutate Pod (driver)<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS
        Note over Webhook: Injects volumes, env vars,<br/>scheduling config, security context,<br/>26 mutation options
        Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Mutated Pod

        Driver->>K8sAPI: Request Executor Pods<br/>443/TCP HTTPS, SA token
        K8sAPI->>Webhook: Mutate Pod (executor)<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS
        Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Mutated Pod
        K8sAPI-->>Driver: Executor Pods running
        Driver->>Executors: Distribute tasks
        Executors-->>Driver: Task results
    end

    rect rgb(230, 255, 230)
        Note over User,ConnectSvc: Flow 2: SparkConnect Server Provisioning
        User->>K8sAPI: POST SparkConnect CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Watch SparkConnect<br/>443/TCP HTTPS, SA token
        K8sAPI-->>Controller: SparkConnect event
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Server Pod + Service + ConfigMap
        Note over ConnectSvc: Ports: 7078/TCP, 7079/TCP,<br/>4040/TCP, 15002/TCP gRPC
        User->>ConnectSvc: Connect via gRPC<br/>15002/TCP
        ConnectSvc->>Executors: Dynamic executor allocation<br/>7078/TCP, 7079/TCP
    end

    rect rgb(255, 245, 230)
        Note over Prometheus,Controller: Metrics Collection
        Prometheus->>Controller: GET /metrics<br/>8080/TCP HTTP, No auth
        Controller-->>Prometheus: Application counts, latency,<br/>executor states
    end
